---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms and Conditions" description="Read the Terms and Conditions of Global Yoga Tips. Learn about user guidelines, digital purchases, and liability limitations.">
  <!-- Top Banner -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-secondary-bg/30 border-b border-border-main/40 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center space-y-4">
      <span class="text-xs uppercase font-bold text-brand-primary tracking-wider">Compliance</span>
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-heading font-semibold text-text-main">Terms and Conditions</h1>
      <p class="text-text-secondary text-base max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Effective date: June 22, 2026. Please read these terms carefully before using our services.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Terms Content -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-white border border-border-main rounded-3xl p-8 sm:p-12 shadow-sm">
      <div class="prose prose-indigo max-w-none text-text-secondary text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed space-y-6">
        <p>
          Welcome to <strong>Global Yoga Tips</strong>! By accessing <a href="https://globalyogatips.com" class="text-brand-primary font-medium hover:underline">globalyogatips.com</a>, you agree to comply with and be bound by the following terms and conditions. If you disagree with any part of these terms, please do not use our website or services.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text-main mt-8 mb-4">1. Intellectual Property Rights</h2>
        <p>
          Unless otherwise stated, Global Yoga Tips and/or its licensors own the intellectual property rights for all material on Global Yoga Tips. All intellectual property rights are reserved. You may access this from Global Yoga Tips for your own personal use subjected to restrictions set in these terms and conditions.
        </p>
        <p>You must not:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li>Republish material or copy blog text from Global Yoga Tips.</li>
          <li>Sell, rent, or sub-license premium digital programs or PDF calendars.</li>
          <li>Reproduce, duplicate, or copy poses metadata and program contents.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text-main mt-8 mb-4">2. Digital Purchases & Access</h2>
        <p>
          Our website offers digital yoga programs, calendars, and premium guides. 
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Immediate Delivery:</strong> Upon successful checkout, your digital program access is immediately provisioned on your User Dashboard.</li>
          <li><strong>Single User License:</strong> Your purchase grants you a personal, non-transferable, and non-exclusive license to use the materials. Sharing login accounts is strictly prohibited.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text-main mt-8 mb-4">3. Medical & Health Disclaimer</h2>
        <p>
          Yoga and breathing exercises involve physical movement which can lead to injury. 
        </p>
        <p class="italic text-text-main font-medium border-l-4 border-brand-primary pl-4">
          The contents of Global Yoga Tips (such as texts, pose breakdowns, blogs, and wellness guides) are for informational and educational purposes only. They do not constitute medical advice. Consult a healthcare professional before starting any new physical exercise routine.
        </p>
        <p>
          By practicing yoga using our guides, you assume full responsibility for your health and physical safety, and release Global Yoga Tips from any liability for injuries incurred.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text-main mt-8 mb-4">4. User Accounts</h2>
        <p>
          When you create an account with us, you must provide information that is accurate, complete, and current at all times. Failure to do so constitutes a breach of the Terms, which may result in immediate termination of your account on our service.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text-main mt-8 mb-4">5. Governing Law</h2>
        <p>
          These terms and conditions are governed by and construed in accordance with local laws, and you irrevocably submit to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts in that location.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text-main mt-8 mb-4">6. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>
          We reserve the right, at our sole discretion, to modify or replace these Terms at any time. We will try to provide at least 30 days notice prior to any new terms taking effect.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text-main mt-8 mb-4">7. Contact Information</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions about these Terms, please contact us:
        </p>
        <p class="font-medium text-text-main">
          Email: <a href="mailto:support@globalyogatips.com" class="text-brand-primary hover:underline">support@globalyogatips.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
